hh3cNS.name: hh3cNS

revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

hh3cNS.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cNS.description: This MIB contains objects to manage the configuration and status information of network traffic statistics. It classifies the IP packets by source IP address, source port, destination IP address, destination port, protocol, ToS and input interface, counts the octets and packets, and sends the statistic information to the specific collector.

hh3cNSActiveTime.name: hh3cNSActiveTime
hh3cNSActiveTime.description: The stream will be aged when the active time of this stream exceeds this value. This object is in minute.

hh3cNSInactiveTime.name: hh3cNSInactiveTime
hh3cNSInactiveTime.description: The stream will be aged when the inactive time of this stream exceeds this value. This object is in second.

hh3cNSVersion.name: hh3cNSVersion
hh3cNSVersion.description: The version of the exported packet, which describes the format of the exported packet. It should export version 5 and version 8 when this object is 5, but it should export version 9 only when the value of this object is 9.

hh3cNSAsType.name: hh3cNSAsType
hh3cNSAsType.description: The number of autonomous system (AS). This object can be origin or peer.

hh3cNSTemplateRefreshRate.name: hh3cNSTemplateRefreshRate
hh3cNSTemplateRefreshRate.description: This object specifies the refresh rate in number of exported packets.

hh3cNSTemplateTimeout.name: hh3cNSTemplateTimeout
hh3cNSTemplateTimeout.description: This object specifies the timeout rate in minutes.

hh3cNSExportVlanOrIfIndex.name: hh3cNSExportVlanOrIfIndex
hh3cNSExportVlanOrIfIndex.description: This object describes the interface index at the exported packet. It can be interface index or vlan id according to the product.

hh3cNSProcessSlotTable.name: hh3cNSProcessSlotTable
hh3cNSProcessSlotTable.description: This table describes the board which can enable network traffic statistics at the switch or router.

hh3cNSProcessSlot.name: hh3cNSProcessSlot
hh3cNSProcessSlot.description: This object describes all boards which can processes network traffic statistics at the switch or router.

hh3cNSExportConfigTable.name: hh3cNSExportConfigTable
hh3cNSExportConfigTable.description: This table describes the configuration of the exported packets.

hh3cNSAggregationType.name: hh3cNSAggregationType
hh3cNSAggregationType.description: The aggregation type. v5Statistics type counts IP packets which have same source IP address, destination IP address, source port, destination port, protocol, ToS, input interface, output interface. AS type counts IP packets which have same source AS, destination AS, input interface and output interface. destinationPrefix type counts IP packets which have same destination AS, output interface, destination mask and destination prefix. sourcePrefix type counts IP packets which have same source AS, input interface, source mask and source prefix. protocolPort type counts IP packets which have same protocol, source port and destination port. prefix type counts IP packets which have same source AS, destination AS, input interface, output interface, source mask, source prefix, destination mask, destination prefix. tosAS type counts IP packets which have same tos, source AS, destination AS, input interface and output interface. tosDestinationPrefix type counts IP packets which have same tos, destination AS, output interface, destination mask and destination prefix. tosProtocolPort type counts IP packets which have same tos, protocol, source port and destination port. tosSourcePrefix type counts IP packets which have same tos, source AS, input interface, source mask and source prefix. tosPrefix type counts IP packets which have same tos, source AS, destination AS, input interface, output interface, source mask, source prefix, destination mask, destination prefix. prefixPort type counts IP packets which have same tos, input interface, output interface, source mask, source prefix, destination mask, destination prefix, source port and destination port.

hh3cNSHostIPAddr.name: hh3cNSHostIPAddr
hh3cNSHostIPAddr.description: The destination IP address of the exported packet. This destination IP address is a NSC (NS Collector) address.

hh3cNSHostPort.name: hh3cNSHostPort
hh3cNSHostPort.description: The destination port of the exported packets. This destination port is a NSC listening port.

hh3cNSSrcIpAddr.name: hh3cNSSrcIpAddr
hh3cNSSrcIpAddr.description: The source IP address of the exported packets.

hh3cNSState.name: hh3cNSState
hh3cNSState.description: The state of aggregation is enabled or disabled.

hh3cNSExportInformationTable.name: hh3cNSExportInformationTable
hh3cNSExportInformationTable.description: This table describes the Information of the exported packets.

hh3cNSExportType.name: hh3cNSExportType
hh3cNSExportType.description: This object is equal to hh3cNSAggregationType.

hh3cNSExportSlot.name: hh3cNSExportSlot
hh3cNSExportSlot.description: This object is equal to hh3cNSProcessSlot.

hh3cNSExportStream.name: hh3cNSExportStream
hh3cNSExportStream.description: This object counts the exported streams.

hh3cNSExportNum.name: hh3cNSExportNum
hh3cNSExportNum.description: This object counts the exported packets.

hh3cNSExportFail.name: hh3cNSExportFail
hh3cNSExportFail.description: This object counts the exported packets which failed to send. The error may be unreachable destination IP address.

hh3cNSSourceSlot.name: hh3cNSSourceSlot
hh3cNSSourceSlot.description: The IP packet will be counted when it is passing through this slot.

hh3cNSSourceIfIndex.name: hh3cNSSourceIfIndex
hh3cNSSourceIfIndex.description: The IP packet will be statistics when it through this interface. This object is equal to ifIndex at ifTable.

hh3cNSDestSlot.name: hh3cNSDestSlot
hh3cNSDestSlot.description: This object is equal to hh3cNSProcessSlot.

hh3cNSDirect.name: hh3cNSDirect
hh3cNSDirect.description: This object describes which packets will be counted. It may be inbound or outbound packets through this interface.

hh3cNSConfigRowStatus.name: hh3cNSConfigRowStatus
hh3cNSConfigRowStatus.description: SNMP Row Status Variable. Writable objects in the table may be written in any RowStatus state.

hh3cNSStatusTable.name: hh3cNSStatusTable
hh3cNSStatusTable.description: This table describes current information of network traffic.

hh3cNSSlot.name: hh3cNSSlot
hh3cNSSlot.description: This object is equal to hh3cNSProcessSlot.

hh3cNSActiveStreamNumber.name: hh3cNSActiveStreamNumber
hh3cNSActiveStreamNumber.description: This object counts current active streams.

hh3cNSTotalStreamNumber.name: hh3cNSTotalStreamNumber
hh3cNSTotalStreamNumber.description: This object counts all statistic streams.

hh3cNSTotalPacketNumber.name: hh3cNSTotalPacketNumber
hh3cNSTotalPacketNumber.description: This object counts all statistic packets.

hh3cNSTotalOctetNumber.name: hh3cNSTotalOctetNumber
hh3cNSTotalOctetNumber.description: This object counts all statistic octets.

hh3cNSMPLSActiveStreamNumber.name: hh3cNSMPLSActiveStreamNumber
hh3cNSMPLSActiveStreamNumber.description: This object counts current active MPLS streams.

hh3cNSMPLSTotalStreamNumber.name: hh3cNSMPLSTotalStreamNumber
hh3cNSMPLSTotalStreamNumber.description: This object counts all statistic MPLS streams.

hh3cNSMPLSTotalPacketNumber.name: hh3cNSMPLSTotalPacketNumber
hh3cNSMPLSTotalPacketNumber.description: This object counts all statistic MPLS packets.

hh3cNSMPLSTotalOctetNumber.name: hh3cNSMPLSTotalOctetNumber
hh3cNSMPLSTotalOctetNumber.description: This object counts all statistic octets of MPLS packets.

hh3cNSResetFlag.name: hh3cNSResetFlag
hh3cNSResetFlag.description: Reset all streams. The default value is disabled, and set this value to enabled when resetting.

hh3cNSResetTime.name: hh3cNSResetTime
hh3cNSResetTime.description: The system up time when stream is reset.
